channel.title: Anyone Know Where I Can Get Free PrintOuts Online Of Drum Sheet Music?
channel.description:
I've been searching for a while now and havent found anything.
Some of you may know that I am quite an experienced drummer. I have finished a lot of my books and wish to move on to some more stuff.
I am looking for Sheet Music. Sheet music isn't all that Tabs and stuff, it is a Stave with all the notations on. I tried using notation software but it just got too tedious and boring. I can't find any good sites which just have a simple printout of ready to use Sheet music. I would write my own but I don't have time at the moment.
Thanks in advaned :)
Chris
